				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250804" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;" >psul</a></span> <span class="odate time_1540740228 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">28 Oct 2018 15:23</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4042404">
									

<p>Many many thanks are owed, and I will add to this post when I'm not exhausted from wrangling listpages modules. Two people however stand out above all others and deserve immediate praise:</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounzie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2167392); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2167392&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1540800367" alt="Rounzie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2167392)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounzie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2167392); return false;">Rounzie</a></span>, who prepared the initial versions of the opening two gifs <em>literally</em> years ago, did an almost perfect job straight off the bat, and then had to wait an incredibly long time for me to get this finished. Rounzie, you are an absolute hero - this could not exist without you, and I'm very grateful.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2303803); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2303803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1540800367" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2303803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2303803); return false;">Cyantreuse</a></span>, who was incredibly patient with my request to produce the burned documents you can see here. Cyantreuse actually produced several drafts, putting up with my nit-picking and pedantry, and then turned around and made even more when I admitted that I'd given unclear instructions as to which records I wanted as physical copies. Thank you incredibly much, Cyantreuse - your work was exactly what this needed, in my opinion.</li>
</ul>
<p>ETA: Even if this doesn't survive, that doesn't mean thanks aren't deserved. My gratitude to all of the following reviewers, all of whom have improved this from where it was originally:</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1540800367" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;">sirpudding</a></span></li>
