<p>I'll be brief on this one: I'm up there with Cimmerian. It came off as boring for me. There's not a lot here for me to care about with these characters, and because of that, it became such a slog to read through. Especially when I kept clicking through the files, hoping that one of them would wrap the whole thing up quickly.</p>
<p>The actual 001 in question didn't really strike a chord with me either. This may be just me, but it felt like I was reading an inverted version of <a href="/end-of-death-hub">End of Death</a>, but without adding anything new to the table.</p>

