														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4043855">
									

<p>That's a great thesis, and I think the issue that many are having is that it's essentially glossed over. I generally love elliptical writing, personally, but you have a big concept here that deserves more exploration (IMO) than some fragments of the Amrita experiments. Especially for an 001 proposal (which, again, is absolutely what your concept deserves), and especially following the meticulous worldbuilding in the first act.</p>

							</div>

								
